2022-xx-xx v0.1.x
    * Add metrics for memory_pages (paging and page faults)
    * Add metrics for disks (blocksize, busy, free, read, size, write)
    
2021-11-17 v0.1.0
    * Add a CHANGELOG.
    * Begin tagging releases.
    * Add support for standard and systemd journal logging.
    * Add a "logging" section to the config to define level and whether to log to the systemd journal or not.
    * Create some new log messages for debugging purposes.
    * Add a configurable timeout for incoming njmon connections (connection_timeout).
    * Put timeouts in a new, "thresholds" section of the config yaml
